        <updateDate>2008-04-09T19:45:56Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Next Generation Homes Act of 2008 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) increase the dollar limits on the new energy efficient home tax credit and revise the energy savings requirements for such credit; and (2) allow a new tax deduction for the purchase of an energy efficient principal residence. </p>]]></text>
